# Plugin-Managed Marker

Agents in this directory are managed and distributed via the ralph-v2 CLI plugin.

**Do NOT publish these agents directly via publish-agents.ps1.**

To publish ralph-v2 CLI agents, use the plugin publisher:
```
pwsh -NoProfile -File scripts/publish/publish-plugins.ps1
```
Or using the workspace command dispatcher:
```
pwsh -NoProfile -File scripts/workspace/run-command.ps1 publish-plugins
```

The plugin bundles all agents, skills, and tools together as a coherent multi-agent system:
  - Plugin source: plugins/cli/ralph-v2/plugin.json
  - Install location: ~/.copilot/state/installed-plugins/ralph-v2
